Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.47,0:00:15.08,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to shine on you,\Nand always like that dazzling sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.38,0:00:18.75,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will defend you\Nfrom all the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.85,0:00:24.75,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the truth from my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.76,0:00:39.54,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If only our hearts could connect,\NI could get you to believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.64,0:00:46.31,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you can't\Nsee it now, don't lose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.48,0:00:54.25,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your kindness won't be in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.08,0:01:01.66,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be carried aloft by the wind\Nto somewhere that isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.06,0:01:08.77,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll cross the sea and cross time,\Nand I know you'll blossom one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.93,0:01:15.41,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever the day,\NI'll be there for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.84,0:01:22.05,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hope I can watch over you\Nlike the sun for all time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.05,0:01:32.02,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the truth from my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.74,0:01:47.47,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The river source should be close.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.55,0:02:00.95,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Am I halfway between\NNayug and Sagu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.17,0:02:25.17,Signs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 25\NCelebration
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.98,0:02:29.38,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Balsa, these flowers\Nare our last hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.18,0:02:32.15,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can you use these\Nto save Chagum?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.02,0:02:35.12,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right. I'll give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.72,0:02:38.42,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do whatever it takes\Nto protect Chagum.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.32,0:02:44.53,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Herbologist, will those\Nflowers work for us as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.83,0:02:47.60,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. If I cast a\Nquick spell on them...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.60,0:02:50.40,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...they should allow\Nanyone to see Nayug.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.93,0:02:53.64,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Give each of us one\Nof those flowers too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.64,0:02:56.14,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We will take up your cause even if...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.14,0:02:58.88,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...we ourselves are\Ntorn apart in the process. Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.38,0:03:04.25,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Thank you. I was\Nplanning to ask for your help anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.01,0:03:06.95,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All of you, please protect Chagum.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.28,0:03:08.52,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Many thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.46,0:03:21.30,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We should simply eat them as is?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.36,0:03:22.33,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.64,0:03:33.94,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, everyone, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.54,0:03:36.35,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To Nayug, where\NChagum has gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.29,0:03:47.49,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Which way?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.19,0:03:49.26,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.40,0:03:59.47,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's no sign of that\Nother egg-eater from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.14,0:04:05.27,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use. I can't see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.04,0:04:08.61,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Does the shigu salua\Nhave no effect on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.91,0:04:11.28,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible that they\Ndon't take effect immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.68,0:04:13.65,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Have faith in the\Nherbologist's magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.65,0:04:16.35,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For now, our top priority is\Ncatching up to Prince Chagum.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.99,0:04:20.92,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What sort of instructions have\Nyou been given by that star reader?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.09,0:04:23.49,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Master Shuga has told us\Nthat if the need should arise...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.49,0:04:28.56,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...to forget about the egg and\Nfocus on protecting the prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.30,0:04:32.84,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see. In a sense, that\Nmight be the right decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.54,0:04:35.54,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For now, let's gamble\Non that decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.64,0:04:38.94,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the egg is born, it's meaningless\Nif Chagum is killed in the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.98,0:04:46.22,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the bleeding\Nhas stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.50,0:05:05.57,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a living creature, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.57,0:05:08.14,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't imagine something\Nlike this coming from our world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.31,0:05:12.64,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.31,0:05:16.15,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get my message?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.41,0:05:21.38,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Balsa and those warriors\Nwent ahead to Saanan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.95,0:05:23.12,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.29,0:05:26.36,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I expected no less from one who\Nreceives Mistress Torogai's teachings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.02,0:05:29.13,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.13,0:05:32.53,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, what\Nhappened to this monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.20,0:05:34.93,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How did you defeat it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.36,0:05:37.93,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I tried eating a shigu salua flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.30,0:05:40.47,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I discovered that the flower's\Npollen acts as a medium...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.47,0:05:44.01,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...and that allows us humans\Nto interact with Nayug.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.44,0:05:45.88,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.48,0:05:48.54,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, pupil of mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.54,0:05:51.25,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, do you have any\Nmore of those flowers?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.25,0:05:55.32,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. But I gave all of them\Nto Balsa and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.42,0:05:56.69,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.12,0:06:01.62,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Young as you are, you might live\Nto see another rebirth of the spirit...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.62,0:06:04.39,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...but this was my last chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.43,0:06:07.93,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, this was\Nmy last chance too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.23,0:06:11.30,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mistress Torogai,\Nwe should make haste as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.17,0:06:14.14,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, protecting the prince is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.27,0:06:15.91,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be in such a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.57,0:06:18.61,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He won't be eaten until dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.52,0:06:30.85,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mistress, that bear...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.69,0:06:33.79,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see it. It's also carrying a...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.76,0:06:38.83,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A Rarunga?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.83,0:06:40.10,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.10,0:06:41.13,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:08.52,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Was that a...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.79,0:07:12.03,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it was probably\Na Nyunga Ro Im egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.03,0:07:15.16,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I suspected that there might\Nbe others besides Chagum.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.16,0:07:20.10,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Being culled like that is probably\Npart of the natural order.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.20,0:07:22.00,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Chagum might also...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:26.74,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right, he might not be safe\Nuntil daybreak after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.01,0:07:29.28,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We need to hurry, star reader!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.28,0:07:31.75,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mistress, take me with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.81,0:07:34.12,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we should take him too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.42,0:07:35.92,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.45,0:07:38.79,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You get on the horse, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.91,0:08:02.85,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's strange. I'm not cold at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.68,0:08:11.69,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So this is Saanan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.26,0:08:21.43,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready to be born, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.72,0:08:44.75,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Balsa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.52,0:08:47.76,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Balsa...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.49,0:08:50.49,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.83,0:08:57.27,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chagum! Stay where you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.23,0:08:59.27,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Balsa...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.74,0:09:00.90,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.97,0:09:02.91,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Spear-wielder, you go on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.14,0:09:05.57,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right! Do what you\Ncan to hold it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.21,0:09:38.31,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chagum!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.78,0:09:41.81,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Balsa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.65,0:09:44.95,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.42,0:09:50.19,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Balsa, I knew you\Nwould come for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.89,0:09:53.56,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I always had faith in you, Balsa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.33,0:10:05.23,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sune! Shoot this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.14,0:10:15.28,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did I get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.09,0:10:33.10,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's a...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.73,0:10:36.13,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In Nayug, this area is under water.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.40,0:10:42.04,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Teacher, this area appears\Nto be underwater in Nayug.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.44,0:10:44.57,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's find a way up to\Nthe top of those cliffs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.05,0:10:56.05,Signs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Moribito Guardian of the Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.66,0:11:06.90,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Have we done it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.08,0:11:23.55,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Balsa! Chagum!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.25,0:11:27.05,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can see the prince?\NWhere is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.18,0:11:30.85,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, I can't see them, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.85,0:11:33.62,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To think my student can\Nsee something that I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.42,0:11:35.76,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How can this be?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.03,0:11:40.83,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The world I know, the world I see...\Nis it no more than half of this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.83,0:11:43.73,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, one ten-thousandth?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.70,0:11:46.24,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.38,0:11:59.92,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No! You mustn't kill the Rarunga!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.98,0:12:03.19,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Chagum?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.79,0:12:05.15,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You want to come out?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.96,0:12:13.26,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can't come out unless\NI'm torn apart by the Rarunga?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.13,0:12:18.37,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hate this... This is something that\NI can't do anything to help with.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.64,0:12:25.67,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mistress, I'll go on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.44,0:12:58.14,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There are more?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.64,0:13:00.34,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Commander, I'm\Nalmost out of arrows.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.84,0:13:03.01,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have much oil left, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.35,0:13:05.01,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Warriors Eight of legend...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:08.02,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...fought on in this situation\Nfor three days and nights.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.12,0:13:10.79,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We may run out of oil,\Nbut thanks to the herbalist...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.79,0:13:13.82,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...we can now confront\Nthese Nayug creatures in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.29,0:13:18.26,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if all we have left are our swords,\Nwe shall fight to the death!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.76,0:13:21.53,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The commander is right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.20,0:13:24.30,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:32.27,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Spear-wielder, take the prince and\Nflee from here while we hold them off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.27,0:13:34.84,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,His escape is our top priority!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.84,0:13:38.81,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. Chagum, hang on.\NWe're getting away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.21,0:13:41.75,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't... I can't leave, Balsa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.45,0:13:44.82,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The egg wants to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.15,0:13:50.06,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If it isn't born here today,\Nit's going to die inside of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.53,0:13:55.23,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let that happen!\NThe egg wants to be born here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.47,0:13:59.97,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Spear-wielder! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.95,0:14:10.81,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sune!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.13,0:14:27.93,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Balsa, I still want to live too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.93,0:14:30.50,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm going to put\Nmyself in fate's hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:33.97,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't live if it means\Nsacrificing your lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.97,0:14:37.31,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...or sacrificing\NYogo's million citizens.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.67,0:14:44.58,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So please, stop fighting!\NI'll do what has to be done!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.48,0:14:47.55,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chagum...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.92,0:14:49.95,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.09,0:14:54.69,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness, don't concern\Nyourselves about us. Just run!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.76,0:14:56.86,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.23,0:15:00.23,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tanda!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.77,0:15:07.04,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like he's\Ncrossed over into Nayug.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.84,0:15:09.71,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Balsa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.21,0:15:14.78,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Chagum!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.88,0:15:18.48,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can extract the egg using\Na spell I learned from Torogai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.65,0:15:21.25,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We need to get Chagum\Nto someplace safe first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.68,0:15:22.82,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You mean it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.82,0:15:30.59,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...200 years ago who made the\Nsame attempt and nearly succeeded.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.33,0:15:34.06,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take your word for it.\NKeep an eye on Chagum for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.80,0:15:42.07,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. There's nothing\Nto worry about, Chagum!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.59,0:16:07.90,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Torogai, is there\Nnothing that we can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.46,0:16:12.50,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing. Just sit quietly\Nand pray for the sun to rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.37,0:16:16.37,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Chagum,\Nyou have to move!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.91,0:16:23.85,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How many of these\Nthings are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.41,0:16:25.61,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's no end to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.12,0:16:32.39,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Torogai?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.32,0:16:38.09,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They seem to be fighting\Na huge number of Rarunga.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.43,0:16:42.56,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.27,0:16:47.97,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose I'll go too...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.25,0:17:00.18,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, follow the\Nspear-wielder's lead!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.38,0:17:29.98,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Balsa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.64,0:17:56.97,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The morning sun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.51,0:18:00.51,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I get it. The sun must\Nhave come up in Sag...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:21.00,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We made it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.43,0:18:25.33,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.07,0:18:28.07,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Balsa...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.68,0:18:34.78,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.21,0:18:36.21,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Torogai!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.95,0:18:41.08,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't hurry, Nayug and\NSagu will separate completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.25,0:18:41.95,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.68,0:18:44.65,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Balsa, give me a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.52,0:18:48.59,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.96,0:18:53.26,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gently reach inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.57,0:19:02.90,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.54,0:19:10.11,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.\NGently take hold of the egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.92,0:19:15.08,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.92,0:19:19.76,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Did you find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.36,0:19:26.80,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.48,0:19:47.35,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That is the egg?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.63,0:19:58.96,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You were safely born, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.86,0:20:03.47,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your wish to live came true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.57,0:20:08.54,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've done it, Tanda, Balsa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.54,0:20:09.74,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.24,0:20:13.64,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Balsa, let me see the egg too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.11,0:20:18.81,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You were very brave...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.75,0:20:21.12,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it's warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.12,0:20:29.09,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, the next order of business...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.09,0:20:30.76,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the nahji.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.19,0:20:37.37,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. If no nahji come, that\Nunprotected egg will probably die soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.90,0:21:07.93,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nahji!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.83,0:21:10.67,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nahji have come!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.23,0:21:14.37,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're right! it's nahji!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.25,0:21:26.98,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're flying off without seeing us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.78,0:21:29.95,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. They'll see us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.17,0:21:46.57,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.87,0:21:49.50,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chagum, what should we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.97,0:21:55.61,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Throw the egg high into the sky,\Nand the nahji will take it in its beak.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.65,0:22:41.52,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now they show up...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.96,0:22:48.36,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed... But now we can\Ngive him a return worthy of a king.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.97,0:23:00.71,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all over. My fight\Nagainst destiny is finally over...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.72,0:23:13.05,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As I sat huddled and alone, holding\Nback the tears on those nights...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.05,0:23:20.20,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When it felt like I was about\Nto succumb to my doubts...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.20,0:23:25.47,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...there you were,\Nat my side before I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.47,0:23:32.81,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was none other than you\Nwho was there for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.81,0:23:47.09,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I keep wishing, "I want to be strong."\NI stumble and hurt myself again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.09,0:23:56.46,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But because I have you to believe in,\NI can get back to my feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.46,0:24:03.24,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I simply want to tell\Nmy dear one, "Thank you. "
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.24,0:24:08.38,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At the top of my lungs,\Nagain and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.38,0:24:16.75,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I call out to my precious loved one.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.75,0:24:20.96,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is my voice reaching you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.96,0:24:29.20,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In this world that always changes,\Nhuman warmth never does.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.20,0:24:39.51,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm certain I sensed the presence\Nof the one that I hold dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.98,0:24:44.78,Signs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Time
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.35,0:24:46.31,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chagum and Balsa have\Nentrusted the egg to the nahji.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.58,0:24:49.99,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What fate awaits them\Nnow that it is all over?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.05,0:24:52.02,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The final episode, "Departure."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.02,0:24:53.49,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The final episode, "Departure."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.02,0:24:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 26\NDeparture
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.99,0:24:57.03,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will never forget you.
